com.intel.icecp.core.security

Interface KeyManagers


  • public interface KeyManagers
    Interface to create and use key managers (IcecpKeyManager), starting from their registered IcecpKeyManagerProviders. In principle, this is similar to (but way simpler than) Channels. Should be used as follows: 

    
 KeyManagers managers = ...; // Some implementation
 ...
 managers.register(SOME_KEY_MANAGER_PROVIDER, provider);
 ...
 IcecpKeyManager km = managers.get(SOME_KEY_MANAGER_PROVIDER, attributes);
 ...
